  <brief_title>Bemiparin Randomized Trial on Bridging Oral Anticoagulants in Invasive Procedures (BERTA Study)</brief_title>
  <acronym>BERTA</acronym>
  <official_title>Multicentric, Randomized, Controlled, Double-blind Clinical Trial to Assess Perioperative Bridging Therapy With Sodium Bemiparin vs Calcium Unfractionated Heparin in Invasive Procedures, Outpatient Surgery and Laparoscopy Surgery in Patients Receiving Long-term Oral Anticoagulant Therapy</official_title>
